Title: Mr. Mercedes (Bill Hodges Trilogy, #1)
Author: Stephen King
My Review: Yet another Stephen King novel to start the week. Only this time, it's not a horror story, not of the mystery and suspense type. More of a race-against-time page-turner, with characters fresh out of the cookie cutter. Which is very unusual coming from Mr. King. I'm sure I'll forget all about it in about a week or two.
